{"tid":1475584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「居屋難抽過六合彩」人生真係好撚悲慘","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T15:02:58.000Z","uid":302597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"43f8fa699a3928d19825041b7eaaa57d4a15969b","tid":1475584,"uid":302597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老竇老母除咗俾啲稅你扣下，<br />\n俾我享受下免費教育，<br />\n喺條街啲地板係你切出嚟之外，<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知我欠咗你政府乜撚嘢，<br />\n做夾心階層真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇綜緩冇公屋冇資助，<br />\n屋企每個月得個少少錢就啱啱好超左額，<br />\n注定呢世捱世界，食自己。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味出到嚟又要欠20幾萬大學學費，<br />\n我成績好之後讀埋Master張單仲唔仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個垃圾社會又要人向上流動，<br />\n但係個環境根本唔容許人咁做。<br />\n<br />\n又要人讀書去改變命運，<br />\n又要輸入外勞，<br />\n俾10幾萬津貼啲大陸人過嚟香港讀大學。<br />\n<br />\n真係屌你老母垃圾政府。<br />\n<br />\n公屋有需要嘅人唔緊要，<br />\n屌你依家俾啲大陸人當貨倉。<br />\n<br />\n居屋又要俾啲綠表同白表五五分帳，<br />\n屌你啦，<br />\n有綠置居點解仲要同我地班又要交稅又冇社會福利嘅夾心階層爭。<br />\n<br />\n我想有個地方住啊！人既基本需求黎架 !<br />\n<br />\n政府你聽唔聽到啊！"},{"pid":"4134fc3ae3a2808803c99e1888bcdefc377a58b2","tid":1475584,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8615ade6a29929341738d61fc17adefee4453d75","tid":1475584,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0fa244775342b88d7b18ece81a6fd5a8162789","tid":1475584,"uid":302597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8615ade6a29929341738d61fc17adefee4453d75","tid":1475584,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"好撚慘啊香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}